text: Kanzelwand is a high mountain on the border between Vorarlberg, Austria and Bavaria, Germany. The summit can be accessed by the Kanzelwand lift, or by hiking. The Fellhorn/Kanzelwand ski area is located here with of pistes and 13 lifts. == References == Category:Allg√§u Alps Category:Geography of Bavaria Category:Mountains of Austria Category:Mountains of Germany Category:Vorarlberg
